Title: Homewrecker Hamilton
Plot: Jenna desperately tries to fix things with Jake, but he is convinced that she is a cheater, with him having photo evidence of Jenna & Matty's makeout session the night before. Tensions between Jake and Matty come out during a pep rally. Meanwhile, Jenna's dad gets her a car and she takes this as a sign of her parent's forthcoming divorce. Ming also finds herself on the outs with the school Asians.
GuestStars: Mike Faiola, Joseph Haro, Wesam Keesh, Kelly Sry, Jessika Van, Sunkrish Bala, Brittany Marie Batchelder, Madison Ford, Howard Henley
